de.uniheidelberg.cl.swp.testacr
Class LingpipeRunner

java.lang.Object
  de.uniheidelberg.cl.swp.testacr.Runner
      de.uniheidelberg.cl.swp.testacr.LingpipeRunner

public class LingpipeRunner
extends Runner

Implementation of the LingPipe coreference algorithm. Requires lingpipe.jar in the build path.
LingPipe returns the coreference pairs as absolute word positions which are mapped to the words in the MMAX2 files to be able to convert the words into CoreferencePairs. Lingpipe download.
